{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_02_01",
  "title": "爆誕！\n魚見プロ\nダクション",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、スーパーに寄ってたら遅れちゃったわ\nブリがお得だったから夕飯はブリ大根に……あら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I stopped by the supermarket and got delayed.\nYellowtails were on sale‚ so let’s have yellowtail radish stew for dinner… Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 12.588322258,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaaan-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃっ！　ちょ、琴乃にすず？　どうしちゃったの？\nねえ！　何か言って！　目を覚ましてよぉ～～っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek! K-Kotono and Suzu? What happened to you?!\nHey! Say something! Wake up~~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8,
      "endTime": 24.0287530899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "怜……逃げ……て……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei… run… away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1999993642,
      "endTime": 27.9092737039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "やつが……やって来ますわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It… is… coming…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0999993642,
      "endTime": 31.766189773799997,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3666.190409600002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4197.688102700003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo001.m4a",
      "text": "ギョ～ッギョギョッギョッ～！\nギョ～ッギョギョギョギョッギョッ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyo! Gyogyo Gyogyo~!\nGyo! Gyogyogyogyogyogyo~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9333356221,
      "endTime": 38.472315438500004,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5733.333333399997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ギョインギョインギョイーン！！\n魚魚っとさんのお出ましギョ～～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyoin Gyoin Gyoin~!\nGyogyo-tto-san has arrived~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6666689555,
      "endTime": 46.7044916789,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo002.m4a",
      "text": "今日からここは『魚見プロ』だギョ！\nそしてわしが新社長の魚魚っとさんだギョ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From this day forward‚ this is 'Gyogyomi Prods‚' gyo!\nAnd I am your new president‚ Gyogyo-tto-san‚ gyo~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9666610717,
      "endTime": 55.2711511611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "は……？　何言ってるの？　そんな勝手なこと出来る訳\nないでしょ！　{user}さん達はどこ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…? What are you talking about? There’s no way you can just\ndo that! Where are {user}-san and the others?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4999946593,
      "endTime": 63.8654825209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "星見漁港のどこかに囚われているらしいの……\n居場所を突き止めるまでは言うことを聞くしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They seem to be held captive somewhere in Hoshimi Fishing Port…\nWe have no choice but to obey until we figure out where they are…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.066661326,
      "endTime": 71.2966387429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo003.m4a",
      "text": "わしは常々思っていた……{user}は\nアイドル達の魅力を引き出せていないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve always thought… {user} can’t\nbring out the full potential of these idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4999946593,
      "endTime": 77.9872507094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo004.m4a",
      "text": "わしは君達を陸だけではなく海中アイドルの最高峰……\n『BIGGYO』に押し上げたいんだギョ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to elevate you all to the pinnacle of not only land idols\nbut also underwater idols… ‘BIGGYO‚’ gyo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.266657257,
      "endTime": 86.01082983010001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "さすが魚魚っと社長です～！　今の時代、陸だけで\nアイドルやっててもトップになんてなれませんよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of President Gyogyo-tto-san~! In this day and age‚\nyou can’t become a top idol just by being a land idol~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.266653188,
      "endTime": 95.26032632180001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～、魚魚っとさん可愛いギョ～\n海中進出頑張るギョ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ Gyogyo-tto-san is so cute‚ gyo~\nI’ll work hard on my underwater debut‚ gyo~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.466653188,
      "endTime": 105.37626756030001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "さくらはまぁ……分かるけど、なんでこころまで\n魚魚っとさんの言いなりなのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For Sakura… I can understand… but why is Kokoro\nobeying Gyogyo-tto-san?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.566653188,
      "endTime": 112.17987321209999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "こころも最初は反発してたんだけど……\n気が付いたらあんな感じになってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro resisted at first…\nbut before we knew it‚ she became like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.366653188,
      "endTime": 119.4052248318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5999865214,
      "endTime": 122.3565170924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo005.m4a",
      "text": "海中での人気をギョーンと穴子登りにするために\nまずはグループ名を変更しておいたギョ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To make your popularity in the underwater world skyrocket like a conger eel‚\nI’ve changed your group names‚ gyo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.566653188,
      "endTime": 130.03563254670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2999824524,
      "endTime": 131.761683178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo006.m4a",
      "text": "『UONITYAiLE』『魚のテンペスト』\n『ギョリーピース』『UoNoir』『魚X』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "FISHINITYAiLE'‚ 'Fish Tempest'‚\nGyori Peace'‚ 'FishNoir'‚ 'Gyoree X'.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9666491191,
      "endTime": 139.0261502902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ウオエル、ウオスト、ギョリピ、ウオノワ……絶妙に\n全部ダサいですけど、ギョリクスが一番キツイですねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fish-aile‚ Gyo-st‚ Gyori-pi‚ FishNoir… They’re all\nexquisitely lame‚ but Gyoree X is the worst.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3333188375,
      "endTime": 150.14384072619998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、サニピも中々よ……コールとかどうするの、これ\nギョリピ！　ギョリピ！　って……はぁ、酷いわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Sunny-pi is pretty bad too… How are we supposed to cheer?\nGyori-pi! Gyori-pi! …Sigh‚ this is awful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.3333188375,
      "endTime": 162.4599170049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ今日から魚見プロみんなで『BIGGYO』\n目指してギョンギョン頑張っていくギョ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ from today onwards‚ everyone at Gyogyomi Prods\nwill work hard and aim for BIGGYO‚ gyo~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6666521709,
      "endTime": 169.88495155980002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "『BIGGYO』なんて聞いたこともないですし\n別になりたくもないですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve never even heard of ‘BIGGYO‚’\nand I don’t want to be one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1666633606,
      "endTime": 175.25999689100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo008.m4a",
      "text": "すずギョン……そんな悲しいこと言わずに\nまずはみんなで心と体を合わせて踊るギョ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-gyo… Don’t say such sad things‚\nand let's all dance together with our hearts and bodies in sync‚ gyo~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.4666633606,
      "endTime": 183.8030805588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-gyogyo009.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に踊ればわしの想いが通じるギョ！\nミュージック、GYO！　GYO！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we dance together‚ my feelings will get through‚ gyo!\nMusic‚ GYO! GYO!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.0999997457,
      "endTime": 191.6640814146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "まさか……これは……『魚魚っとさん音頭』！？\nくっ……踊りたくないのに……体が勝手に……！",
      "translations": {
